        "subject": "LU-5644 clio: wait on cll_holds instead of cll_users",
        "message": "LU-5644 clio: wait on cll_holds instead of cll_users\n\nIn cl_locks_prune(), we should wait on cll_holds instead of cll_users\nbecause that's the real condition for clio to get rid of a cl_lock.\nOtherwise, it will get into an inifinite loop.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ib453131cbb57efc10222546513ea9d073185da4c\n"
      },
